\fs58 \cf0 Summary\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl480\sa382

\b0\fs26 \cf0 The GB SciCam is a Universal iOS app for iPhone and iPad. It receives its data from a REST server that provides an API layer to the archived data from the SiteProxy software.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl560\sa254

